precis:
Amendments to the ATLANTIC FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1985 which revoke those
provisions that regulate lobster trap escape mechanisms and impose limits
on the number of tended lines used in bluefin tuna fishing, which are to be
replaced by placing conditions on fishing licences.
